WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.350 --> 00:00:04.446
NULL:  Every gap, every shortcut, every forgotten door -

2
00:00:04.446 --> 00:00:05.700
I will find it.

3
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:09.028
VEGA:  Not tonight. Even if you slip in, you

4
00:00:09.028 --> 00:00:10.747
will not move unseen.

5
00:00:11.047 --> 00:00:13.176
NOVA:  Because someone's watching?

6
00:00:13.476 --> 00:00:16.473
VEGA:  Because the watchtowers never sleep.

7
00:00:17.523 --> 00:00:21.161
NULL:  I slipped a careless credential past your wall.

8
00:00:21.161 --> 00:00:23.173
Now I move in the shadows.

9
00:00:23.473 --> 00:00:27.795
VEGA:  Shadows don't last here. The watchtowers never sleep.

10
00:00:28.845 --> 00:00:31.988
VEGA:  Layer two assumes someone got in. Now we

11
00:00:31.988 --> 00:00:34.817
see them, stop the rot, and respond.

12
00:00:35.117 --> 00:00:40.028
Three families keep watch: Audit, System Integrity, and

13
00:00:40.028 --> 00:00:41.635
Incident Response.

14
00:00:42.685 --> 00:00:45.720
NOVA:  AU, SI, and IR. The eyes, the immune

15
00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:48.164
system, and the firefighters.

16
00:00:49.214 --> 00:00:52.886
VEGA:  The Chronicler, Audit and Accountability.

17
00:00:53.186 --> 00:00:57.233
VEGA:  It records every footstep, so no deed goes

18
00:00:57.233 --> 00:00:57.908
