21
00:01:06.980 --> 00:01:09.309
NOVA:  What exactly is a 'log'?

22
00:01:09.609 --> 00:01:13.112
VEGA:  A diary the system keeps. A Windows Event

23
00:01:13.112 --> 00:01:16.102
Log, a syslog, a tool like Splunk -

24
00:01:16.102 --> 00:01:16.956
same idea.

25
00:01:18.006 --> 00:01:21.303
VEGA:  AU-2 chooses what's worth logging.

26
00:01:21.603 --> 00:01:24.929
NULL:  So I'll just delete the logs when I'm

27
00:01:24.929 --> 00:01:25.378
